# ORIG TITLE    From behind bars to heavy metal – Ai Wei Wei sings . 
# ORIG CONTENT  Dissident Chinese artist Ai Wei Wei has made his first foray into the world of music with the release of the first single from his debut album called “Divine Comedy” inspired by his detention in 2011. The video depicts his 81 days in prison and, along with the rest of the six-track album, criticises the Chinese authorities. 
